# GreenLink v2 Cursor Rules

## Project Structure
- Monorepo using pnpm and Turbo
- Apps: `apps/web` (3000), `apps/admin` (3001), `apps/driver` (3002)
- Packages: `packages/ui`, `packages/lib`

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- React 18+
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Lucide React (Icons)
- Shadcn UI (Component Library)

## Guidelines
- Use Functional Components with TypeScript
- Prefer Server Components where possible (Next.js App Router)
- Use strict type safety
- Follow SOLID principles
- Maintain clean, documented code
